message.entry: Colormap element out of range. RGB intensities should be normalized on the range 0.0 <= intensity <= 1.0. Scale the colormap by \"max(max(<colormap>))\" to normalize it.
Dithermap element out of range. RGB intensities should be normalized on the range 0.0 <= intensity <= 1.0. Scale the colormap by \"max(max(<dithermap>))\" to normalize it.
